{"id":260623,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/11/维权网-湖南永州村民周三梅4年拿不到土地补偿款/","date":"2012-11-02T01:45:48Z","modified":"2012-11-02T01:45:48Z","title":"维权网 | 湖南永州村民周三梅4年拿不到土地补偿款","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员钟剑报道）湖南省永州市宁远县冷水镇十里铺村村民周三梅，现年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">44</span><span>岁，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年宁远县开发办征收土地，按规定她家</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>口人应该分到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9160</span><span>元的土地补偿款，却始终没有得到。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>周三梅多次找到村委会，要求给付应得的土地补偿款，村委会却以种种理由拒绝支付。周三梅便开始上访县委、县政府、冷水镇党委、县信访办。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>今</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日周三梅再次到永州市信访局反映，永州市信访接待中心也进行了督办。但是到目前为止，她依然没有拿到补偿款。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>周三梅认为，十里铺村委会以不正当理由拖欠、侵占她家的土地补偿款，是严重的违法行为，已严重侵犯了她家的合法权益。周三梅希望各界关注，维护她一家人的合法权益。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>周三梅手机</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15200976277<a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"_GoBack\"></a></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-5539091207439410356?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","au